    <div class="card">
      <p class="mt0">Built in 1885 and deeded to the village in 1947, Rous Lench Village Hall hosts public events and is available for hire.</p>
      <p><a href="https://rouslench.com/">Visit the Rous Lench website &rarr;</a></p>
